{"tid":1634792,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（轉載自高登）見大家講Hk01咁開心，不如又燒埋經濟日報","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T05:52:58.000Z","uid":201464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6745ba88fc7eab57cd0b5a8f8a7b827dfe558613","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7128041/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7128041%2Fpage%2F1&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=a70ad206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7128041/page/1</a><br />\n前者係黑手套，已經污糟晒<br />\n後者係白手套，仲未完全搜晒證，但我sure一點係topick個班底半年幾前同連登已經deal左D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔淨在爆多樣野<br />\n<br />\n香港最大yahoo agency個間野係連登主要既廣告代理，間野呢4年起左幾十個content farm出黎，幾乎一有01同連登post要吹風，佢就用呢個network share到周圍都係<br />\n<br />\nD content farm要用yahoo廣告搵食，同埋本身佢地對連登都係好感&gt;反感，久而久之就做到好似連登一呼百應咁<br />\n<br />\n比多個Hints大家<br />\n<br />\n講埋先，間野唔係GURU，個老世係don mak個細佬<br />\n<br />\n大家自己估下啦<br />\n<br />\n之前見高登有post講過，咪好奇去八下有咩料，點知又八到D野返黎<br />\n而家係未confirm經濟日報個邊究竟接頭人同落order既人係咩人，野就已經做緊<br />\n<br />\nYAHOO個agent就都有D人知咩事架啦，但知既人唔會講，既得利益者話知你死，唔知既人當然一直都唔可能會知<br />\n<br />\n早前6月中個陣已經覺得唔對路，成個運動既氣氛似係想瓦解香港既「建制／地產勢力」多過「抗共」，內部互鬥多過真係反抗極權<br />\n有D說話太早講無咩用，但時間會證明一D野<br />\n<br />\n包括地產商／地鐵／警隊／三司呢類，唔排除係有更上面既人想佢地死，同時又叫佢地死頂，先會做到每步必錯<br />\n呢種每步必錯既局面係一個現代都市黎講根本無可能發生<br />\n唔好再拎烏克蘭同法國黃背心去做對比，其一我地無真正既民主，其二我地「媒體口中主流」對抗緊既「敵人」，分分鐘只係bigger boss整出黎既稻草人咁，借力打力互相消耗<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭同法國政府有自主權，尚且見反成咁，點都唔會火上加油<br />\n香港真係完全相反，新X基傳訊部佢地都焦頭爛額到一個點，明明下層不停想救火，朝早開完會，唔知點解下晝就無啦啦要加多幾條柴去燒<br />\n<br />\n好多暗位比我覺得呢場運動真係計算左好多先發生，利用盡包括可以利用既人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>To be continued</strong>"},{"pid":"66dcce9208f59344f5f9acbb8a3dd960bfca1eda","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"3c6314b35f11bbf4942303127ddc323e90dde12b","tid":1634792,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文見此：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"dc164176c060c4a309a41cecdaa9e663e4d11689","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"4c95c14c5985c092b2f105db05f4e7b29836299b","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"a3a7046f8cb82a342225d9a5d698a3ee002ab0e2","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"cfda75483099f566e083c6d1fe11e4be11710f62","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"8c5c2b1423c4bc5abcccab3cb30dd66d5063be39","tid":1634792,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3db76b78e2a579e5ad01991a49686f13ed74d13","tid":1634792,"uid":77526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"值得諗諗"},{"pid":"24c1d0d9879e3faa2a26a28cb8fb628340221018","tid":1634792,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"7b6c5a882099e9c42328e3e66c4e637e128cdad0","tid":1634792,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"[為雙10感謝祭打開序幕]呢間餐廳大家一定要試下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2667b46960bfbeebecbc08d33eccab1fc22ff360","tid":1634792,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}